Dear Mr AZ Patient 3,

Mr Az Pro 1 has invited you to access the medical information of Mr John Patient so you can help manage their health.

Message from Mr Az Pro 1

Please consider being my carer

To accept this invitation, click this link:

http://pkb-frontend-3/patient/accept.action?invitationId=a24e8a74-f0cf-4e79-b935-842376996519&e=az.patient.3%40pkbtest.com

You are receiving this notification because you are a carer. To log in and review the people you care for, please click this link: "http://pkb-frontend-3/patient/myDependents.action?tab=invitations&subTab=dependents"

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Log into your record to manage your care and those whom you care for.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team
